---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Me">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <Sidebar />
      <div class="content">
        <img src="/assets/images/5ec214ea5013c55f509cdda7_company_logo.png" alt="Company logos" style="width:100%; border-radius:5px; margin-bottom:20px;" />

        <h1>Where Do I Fall on the Curve?</h1>

        <div style="margin-bottom:20px;">
          <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/james-chenyang-wang" class="btn">My LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="/assets/files/5b132152804c1fbf21d5b9f6_Resume-James-Wang.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn">My Resume</a>
        </div>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19d76b151be048696ff0db_UNADJUSTEDNONRAW_thumb_b8cb.jpg" alt="Hallgrimskirkja, Iceland" class="about-photo" />
        <div class="about-caption">(Hallgrimskirkja, Iceland 2017)</div>

        <h3>Dante's Divine Comedy is my favorite epic of all times. I read its 3 cantiche&mdash;Inferno, Purgatorio, and Paradiso, front to back, 3 times. It challenges the limit of my imagination and makes me ponder if life has a meaning.</h3>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19d76baa90055229e2cae3_l_WTlbMRTM6LpC3wCueZbA_thumb_af48.jpg" alt="Dante's Death Mask" class="about-photo" />
        <div class="about-caption">(Dante's Death Mask, Florence 2017)</div>

        <h3>I often debate whether soccer or tennis is my #1 favorite sport. I love embracing my sweaty teammates, and crushing my unwieldily opponents.</h3>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19d76b844733964b1ce9e6_u1vX5eDTSumJBNA1zIZt0Q_thumb_86cb.jpg" alt="Championship soccer team" style="width:100%; border-radius:3px; margin:15px 0;" />
        <div class="about-caption">(Championship member: Nanjing Mayor's Cup 2015)</div>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19d76bec6f20ea8678e724_2j0yA7j0Qo2VByWhXUQ2XA_thumb_a4ed.jpg" alt="Tennis coach in Serbia" class="about-photo" />
        <div class="about-caption">(With my tennis coach in Serbia, 2016)</div>

        <h3>I stand up for injustice,&hellip;, a few times. Human migration and refugee crisis is one area I care deeply. Although far from making an impact, it helps me believe the world is becoming a better place, with the angelic friends I made along the road.</h3>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19eba8b242416a2f7d6e3a_IMG_7829.jpg" alt="Book Drive for Hope Institute" style="max-width:526px; width:100%; border-radius:3px; margin:15px 0;" />
        <div class="about-caption">(Book Drive for Hope Institute for Migrant Children, Nanjing, China, 2013-2014)</div>

        <div class="video-embed">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qBuircLH-ZI" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="about-caption">(Aiding Middle Eastern refugees at Info Park, Belgrade, Serbia, Summer 2016)</div>

        <h3>At the end of the day, I believe in the business world. And I believe in the internet innovations. Reading business cases keeps me up at night, while solving my business problems gets me up in the morning.</h3>

        <img src="/assets/images/5b19d76bf61624ba5304677c_6xT4b1uQQXmwdzok7PB0kA_thumb_bae0.jpg" alt="Business" style="max-width:522px; width:100%; border-radius:3px; margin:15px 0;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
